== Installing from a git checkout ==
$ autoreconf -i
$ ./configure
$ su -
$ make
$ make install

NOTE: if installing on MacOSX, autoreconf may not be present. Follow instructions here to install autoconf, automake and libtools packages and then proceed with autoreconf: http://jsdelfino.blogspot.co.uk/2012/08/autoconf-and-automake-on-mac-os-x.html

== Installing from a released source tarball ==

$ tar xzvf fasta_grep-1.0.tar.gz
$ cd fasta_grep-1.0
$ ./configure
$ make
$ su -
$ make install